According to Reference Manual:
 000b - Divide by 1
 001b - Divide by 1
 010b - Divide by 2
 011b - Divide by 3
 100b - Divide by 4
 101b - Divide by 5
 110b - Divide by 6
 111b - Divide by 7

So only need increase rdiv by 1 when the register value is 0.

